body_html:
It's possible there was performance regression in parse_example

For this to get resolved there needs to be at minimum a reproducible example, and ideally, some investigation of the cause of the slowness

  1. It takes 240 secs, how much do you expect it to take? Is it possible that it's as as fast as it can be? Similar discussion with parse_csv slow
    #11713

  2. gperftools profile to show where time is spent is useful, like here
    #3009 (comment)

body:
It's possible there was performance regression in parse_example 

For this to get resolved there needs to be at minimum a reproducible example, and ideally, some investigation of the cause of the slowness

1. It takes 240 secs, how much do you expect it to take? Is it possible that it's as as fast as it can be? Similar discussion with parse_csv slow
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/11713

2.  [gperftools](https://github.com/gperftools/gperftools) profile to show where time is spent is useful, like here
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/3009#issuecomment-228867287
